# code-frontend.diff — agent-loop Observability Dashboard

Scope: React 19 + TypeScript SPA scaffolded with Vite, implementing the Ops Health
and Diagnostic screens per `.build/design.md` / `.build/spec.md`. Plus the three
additive backend endpoints the UI consumes (`src/dashboard-api.ts` + minimal wiring
in `routes.ts` / `daemon-api.ts` / `daemon.ts`).

## What was built
- App shell: `QueryClientProvider` + `LoopStreamProvider` (single WS owner), TopBar
  (status pill, uptime, WS-liveness dot), TabNav (Ops Health | Diagnostic).
- `useLoopStream` hook + provider: WS /ws with exponential backoff, requestAnimationFrame
  batching of buffered messages, ref-backed store drained once per frame, primes the
  TanStack Query cache on `state_change`/`child_status_change`, and flips to a poll
  fallback flag after repeated WS failures (design §0 principles 2-5).
- 8 TanStack Query hooks (one per endpoint): state, metrics, history, task, loops,
  health-score, time-series, checkpoint. 404 -> null so new endpoints degrade gracefully.
- Ops Health: HealthScoreCard (Recharts gauge), MetricCardGrid (Pass/Fail/Error donut,
  Duration, Throughput, Queue — React.memo), LiveTimeSeriesStrip (uPlot), ActiveLoopsPanel,
  MiniEventFeed, BudgetBanner.
- Diagnostic: IndicatorsPanel (triggers + uPlot series), filterable virtualized EventFeed
  (TanStack Virtual), virtualized HistoryTable (TanStack Table + Virtual) with row -> drawer,
  TaskDetailDrawer, CheckpointBar.
- Backend `src/dashboard-api.ts`: `computeHealthScore`, `createTsRing` (live ring
  appended each 2s `state_change`), `loadCheckpointState`, and `handleDashboardApi`
  dispatcher (returns null for non-dashboard routes). Wired via one delegation block in
  `routes.ts`; `DaemonAPI.tsRing` added; daemon appends a throughput sample per tick.

## Build & verification
- `cd dashboard && bun install && bun run build` -> emits `src/dashboard/index.html` +
  assets (Vite `base:'./'`, `outDir:'../src/dashboard'`). The daemon serves it at
  `GET /dashboard` with no daemon change (`src/daemon.ts:199`).
- Frontend typecheck: `bunx tsc --noEmit` clean.
- Frontend tests (vitest): 8 pass (api 404->null, ApiError, param build; RAF batching).
- Backend test `__tests__/dashboard-api.test.ts`: 8 pass (ring eviction, score grades,
  dispatcher routing + 404).
- Root `bun test`: green except 3 pre-existing, unrelated failures
  (`agent-loop-mcp`, `executeWithTimeout`, `loop-factory/notes`) — none touch the
  dashboard/daemon/routes/metrics code.

## NOT in this diff (generated, rebuild to reproduce)
- `src/dashboard/` built assets (produced by `bun run build`); excluded to keep the
  diff readable. Run the build to regenerate them for the daemon.
- `dashboard/node_modules` excluded.

## Acceptance mapping
§7.1 build passes (vite build -> src/dashboard) · §7.2 daemon serves /dashboard ·
§7.3 all P0 metrics render · §7.4 diagnostic (virtualized feed/table + drawer) ·
§7.5 three endpoints wired (return JSON) · §7.6 bun test still green (additive).

